{"tid":2296260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「殺狗抗疫發獎金！」　東莞社區獵殺公告...看了讓人頭皮發麻","createTime":"2020-11-22T10:35:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T13:10:39.000Z","uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d79e617e575aae4ccf061a08258fa600f276dc5e","tid":2296260,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T10:35:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4731/d4731247.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4731%2Fd4731247.jpg&h=b0a0f07c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲大陸東莞社區發出獵殺通告，禁止飼主放養寵物，一律殺無赦，被批殘忍。（圖／翻攝 星島網）<br />\n<br />\n大陸爆發新冠肺炎（COVID-19）後，不少社區推出「禁止遛狗令」。近日網路流傳一份來自大陸東莞社區通告，看得讓人頭皮發麻！管委會揚言住戶如果放養寵物將被活活打死，還號召鄰居參與，可獲得300到200不等的獎金。（單位；人民幣，同下）<br />\n根據星島網指出，東莞的社區發出最新通告，管委會宣稱為了防疫，要加強寵物狗的管理，發現有放養行為一律「殺無赦」！ 通告內容規定，社區嚴禁放養狗隻、嚴禁帶狗隻到公共場所大小便、嚴禁圈養狗隻。規定十分殘忍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4731/4731246.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4731%2F4731246.jpg&h=d62679d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲大陸東莞社區發出獵殺寵物通告，號召鄰居參與拿獎金。（圖／翻攝微博 交通事兒）<br />\n<br />\n如果發現放養行為，一律進行捕殺，管委會還鼓勵居民共同參與管理，捕殺一隻放養流浪狗，15斤以上大型犬可獲300元獎勵，換算大約是1300多台幣，15斤以下可得200元獎勵。如果發現有人帶狗隻在公共場所大小便，將停發季度股金分紅及環境獎勵金，如屬出租戶，由屋主承擔，有關措施會5日正式執行。<br />\n這則「獵殺通告」也引起大陸網民熱論，不少人留言怒罵通告不合理，太粗暴野蠻。認為「如果人守規律，狗就不會有無妄之災」、「人類的錯誤卻要去屠殺其他弱小生靈？」也有網友稱「放養就該打死」、「獎勵得太少」但，大部分支持留言的比較少。"},{"pid":"efbc14977007e67cb2bc623b1c3c00d436b1b920","tid":2296260,"uid":185656,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T10:36:42.000Z","msg":"黑警triggered"},{"pid":"df4575a550380e70571008a1c7f5966be263466e","tid":2296260,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T10:37:21.000Z","msg":"衲dee<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaaf2c579a649033e72198c66b836bbae27e554a","tid":2296260,"uid":290118,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T10:41:50.000Z","msg":"我入到嚟⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係以為講緊另一啲狗"},{"pid":"8793071829635594224938f78fd6bcee3f4a9b6a","tid":2296260,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T10:47:38.000Z","msg":"殺撚晒堆支那人對環境仲好喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecceb1438029b9bc0d248979c7d3a951f1e83879","tid":2296260,"uid":127425,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T11:33:55.000Z","msg":"我要北上搵銀了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8e3f0c6aca755edb7f3f98a4d86ee8b9bd6f4b1","tid":2296260,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T12:16:08.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"fcbed299083acd3ed39d44711b1088a6764c4ac2","tid":2296260,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T12:18:35.000Z","msg":"殺一隻狗$300<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d17ff302b8fc50ac8565071f807ba13237764c","tid":2296260,"uid":90660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T12:19:32.000Z","msg":"殺狗抗疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e0fc2090a19c6cb9c1852580143d01d918f45e4","tid":2296260,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T12:35:44.000Z","msg":"2020 2月"},{"pid":"3cc632fa201847cdcb66c07cc2857eb2da1fc3c5","tid":2296260,"uid":261478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T12:44:08.000Z","msg":"警局入面有好多狗<br />\n為左對抗武漢肺炎<br />\n支持香港政府帶頭殺狗<br />\n由其是無number果D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:中共黨員，絕對支持習近平永續帝位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f9b5ead23fa762735572f194d0adf2dac2698c0","tid":2296260,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T12:45:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1acce1668f75c245a9426a37e3b9c1c2018652f","tid":2296260,"uid":373900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d79e617e575aae4ccf061a08258fa600f276dc5e","tid":2296260,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T10:35:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4731/d4731247.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4731%2Fd4731247.jpg&h=b0a0f07c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲大陸東莞社區發出獵殺通告，禁止飼主放養寵物，一律殺無赦，被批殘忍。（圖／翻攝 星島網）<br />\n<br />\n大陸爆發新冠肺炎（COVID-19）後，不少社區推出「禁止遛狗令」。近日網路流傳一份來自大陸東莞社區通告，看得讓人頭皮發麻！管委會揚言住戶如果放養寵物將被活活打死，還號召鄰居參與，可獲得300到200不等的獎金。（單位；人民幣，同下）<br />\n根據星島網指出，東莞的社區發出最新通告，管委會宣稱為了防疫，要加強寵物狗的管理，發現有放養行為一律「殺無赦」！ 通告內容規定，社區嚴禁放養狗隻、嚴禁帶狗隻到公共場所大小便、嚴禁圈養狗隻。規定十分殘忍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4731/4731246.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4731%2F4731246.jpg&h=d62679d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲大陸東莞社區發出獵殺寵物通告，號召鄰居參與拿獎金。（圖／翻攝微博 交通事兒）<br />\n<br />\n如果發現放養行為，一律進行捕殺，管委會還鼓勵居民共同參與管理，捕殺一隻放養流浪狗，15斤以上大型犬可獲300元獎勵，換算大約是1300多台幣，15斤以下可得200元獎勵。如果發現有人帶狗隻在公共場所大小便，將停發季度股金分紅及環境獎勵金，如屬出租戶，由屋主承擔，有關措施會5日正式執行。<br />\n這則「獵殺通告」也引起大陸網民熱論，不少人留言怒罵通告不合理，太粗暴野蠻。認為「如果人守規律，狗就不會有無妄之災」、「人類的錯誤卻要去屠殺其他弱小生靈？」也有網友稱「放養就該打死」、「獎勵得太少」但，大部分支持留言的比較少。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:10:39.000Z","msg":"呢個要推上國際俾動物撚、素食撚左膠睇<br />\n順便幫班蟈人宣傳埋獵殺啲狗係為左賣狗肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收錢捉狗賣去狗肉節斬件食狗肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H39QJxr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH39QJxr.jpg&h=81cbb2c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R1AcWSs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR1AcWSs.jpg&h=190cf215&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ntPtvcq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FntPtvcq.jpg&h=e476daae&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rRWvJxq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrRWvJxq.jpg&h=cb040d93&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EsJJ3xr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEsJJ3xr.jpg&h=5fe3edef&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}